      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 22.85714285714286,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "1 - By storing the value in the hashmap \n\n2 - then calculate the sum of twins pairs  \n\n3 - then find the max",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
